title: 10 Vista business OEM serials
description:
As part of the UK governments 'get people back to work' initiative, I am required to attend a training centre once a week. 

All the computers in the centre have Windows XP installed, but have genuine Vista business stickers on all the machines, which I photographed.

I've been told that none of these keys have been activated with Microsoft, so I offer these to you guys in the hope that they can be some use.

Wouldn't it be hilarious if they upgraded one day and none of these serials worked! Bwahahahaha!


-------------------------------------------------

This torrent contains 10 genuine Windows Vista Business keys (JPGs) taken from government BTCV training centre machines.
